### Connectivity Check

After opening the base URL, if the page title or body contains a **CloudFront 403 error** (e.g. "403 ERROR", "The request could not be satisfied", "Request blocked"), **stop the entire regression run immediately**. Do not attempt any scenarios. Tell the user:

> ❌ **Cannot reach the Dev environment.** The CloudFront CDN is returning a 403. Please connect to the VPN and try again.

Then exit — do not proceed with any further steps or Jira updates.

## Report Results
After all scenarios complete, produce a structured test report with:
- Total scenarios: passed / failed / skipped
- Failed scenario details with screenshots
- Bugs to file (with reproduction steps from the failed scenario)

Transition the domain Subtask:
- **All pass** → transition to Done
- **Any failure** → leave In Progress, add a summary comment listing failures

Transition the run Task to Done only when all domain Subtasks are Done.
